Prowl doesn't have a comm on him right now.

::Kluster/Shredder::

Kluster frowns, the scanners reporting bots firing and getting away 
from the CF. He glances at the reports, but then frowns again as the 
Cybertronian Fire intercept's Magmatron's transmission to Shredder.

He looks over at Shredder, who'se eyes were wide.

"Ha!" Shredder says, shutting off his comm to make sure Magmatron 
couldn't hear him, "He thought I'd come back after how he turned on 
me."

He looks at Kluster, "I'll keep my comm open for any more 
transmissions from him, it could give us valueble data."

Shredder knew that he couldn't reply to Magmatron in the Maximal 
base. He would do it as soon as he got out.
